column2: I need you and Lamar out in the field. Some of our customers have foolishly over-stretched themselves again with their credit schedule. And you wonder why America is in a crisis!
Answer you phone dog! where r u? We gotta check out Bertolt Beach House for Simeon.
Am I dreaming or did I just see you and lamar tearing up the del perro freeway on some sick wheels??
Employee of the month? Now that's some bullshit.
What the hell happened with that bike? Why must you make a simple job so complicated?
That was wild down at Vespucci, dog. We need to ask Yetarian for a pay rise.
Where's all this supposed money from this supposed job you've got? Cause I ain't seen a cent come my way. It's your grandmother's fault for spoiling you too much! Classic only child.
U hear about that Vagos kid gettin clipped down at Vespucci Beach? People saying it was a Families hit.
I never thought I'd say thus but I miss you and the rest of the Chamberlain crew.
Send u a postcard bitchz coz lamar davis is goin places!!!

If you refuse speak to me directly, this is the only way. Stop acting like a spoiled brat and be thankful for what you have. I have created a monster.
My parents are driving me CRAZY. I have to get my own place soon.
Gary's different. He kisses me like it means something rather than just a token 10 seconds before trying to get my bra off like all the other guys.
I really think Gary might be the one :)
I take it all back. Maybe you will be famous... for having the most cavernous gaper in history.

Great session today. Always a pleasure working with you. And I WILL call you Amanda :)
You'd never know @Amanda De Santa was in her 40s ;)
What's with you aunt? Walking around like a duck hollering about womanhood?
Street brakes, sport brakes, race brakes. We got it all at Los Santos Customs.
Ok that thing with D and the phone call maybe not my smartest move ever but that's how I do it F! When you got apache blood you fly a little closer to the sun!.

Holla at me whenever u and franklin put each others dicks down for a minute

So yeah sorry about the boat I was just trying to use my initiative and make a contribution to the finances like you keep saying I need to. Gotta get creative in a recession! At least I was outside right??? That home invader turned out to be pretty cool btw.
My mom won't let Gary stay the night. Why's she the only one who gets to be the whore? She is such a dictator!

So that boat thing didn't work out. Lucky for me my dad's a lunatic or I could be dead right now!
Oh and I did I mention that my dad is now best friends with the burglar who broken into our house? Don't even ask.
My schedule's wide open let me know when he isn't around.
Lot of talk in here about Chilli D - stay away from that shit.
That shit at the warehouse today that's what happens when you try to be something you're not. Don't try to run before you can walk especially in shoes that you aint big enough to fill yet.
Me, you and Stretch back in business! CGF makin it count baby!
What's this about you saying I set you up? Keep runnin your mouth like that you gonna take a fall.
Remember that threeway with the girl with the lazy eye from the pizza place? We didn't know who she was telling to do what! Hahahahaha! #oldfriends Can you lend me $200?
Wen r we gettin blunted???

That mess at the plant aint on me. Your eye's off the ball. Don't get it twisted CGF is in your DNA you can't change that. So whatever this Forum shit is you and Franklin got going it need to get gone. Keep your boy in check.
Take your finger off the pause button coz I'm out bitchzzzzz! Bolingbroke Prison I hope I aint seein you again no time soon.
When are we going out on the prowl for ladies assuming you still like them?

Don't blame Kyle. I thought we had an understanding??? It can't be one rule for you and another for me. What about those three charges to Honkers last month? You think I don't look at the bank statements? Anyway, let's move on... you know, for the kids and all that.
Listen bud, sorry again. Not cool. Again, goes without saying that I'll comp the session. No hard feelings I hope.
My insecure jealous husband takes his next victim...
The tennis guy? Way to go, mom. Real classy.

I saw a suspicious-looking black man hanging around the De Santa house again. I don't know whether it's the economic downturn or what, but this community doesn't feel as safe as it should any more given how much money I spent to live here.
And another possessive midlife crisis psycho tries to kill me! I am so over this!

Good hanging out today at Vespucci Beach, pop. I think. Although I'm kind of weirded out by it. And I have these scary pains in my thighs. Let's just do something inside next time where my glandular issues and your angers issues won't get us in trouble?

I hate you. How could you embarrass me like that? Why do you have to be such a fucking caveman? A couple of the guys on that yacht were legitimate industry people. Are you trying to ruin the rest of my life? Do anything like that again and I really will get into porn just to punish you.
So seriously what is the new TV situation? Because this needs to get rectified like asap.
I'm officially over Gary. I hope he dies in a horrible accident. And for you other girls out there, he's like a cashew nut, so don't even bother.
I have the most psycho dad in the world. He just dragged me away from the coolest yacht party EVER!! I seriously think he needs some kind of mental intervention.
Fuck you and your crazy dad. You owe me a new Seashark. Good luck getting into the industry now
So now you're doing porn too. Congratulations on exceeding my skanky expectations once again.
In weird 'De Santa' family news... Dad smashes TV in blind rage, Jimmy + Dad go on gay bike ride, Dad hijacks a boat and steals sea shark. Oh, and Tracey does porn (ok no news there).
You weasely little shit telling dad about the party on the yacht. Get a life of your own!
I was driving through Vinewood earlier and saw a guy dressed like a moronic teenager who looked the spit of you! I must be going crazy!
Ok, I'd say you've atoned for that decade of poor friendship. How ironic we're both on Lifeinvader? Too soon?
Wow, you really made yourself hard to find with the whole family on here.
So tripped out about Jay Norris! I was all ready to camp out in line for that mobile device!
fyi dad just attacked those porno guys you rented the house to last summer
Long time no see. The years have clearly been kinder to you than they have to Michael. You've got the body you never had when you were 20.
Lifeinvader's new product certainly exploded onto the market.
Why did I buy all that Lifeinvader stock??? So dumb.

Shoplifting? Isn't one criminal enough in this parenting duo?
Nice job. A real gem, you might say! Just like the good old days.
Something is very wrong. My Dad has friends over and he's in a really good mood. I think I might be trapped in a parallel universe.
NO!!!! My favorite jewelry store got robbed!
You'll pay for what happened to Johnny. All of you.
Our own airstrip! Trevor Philips Industries! We're going places!
Sorry about your statue. You were incredible today Trevor. I wish I was a trained airforce pilot like you!

I am pleased to report that my new requisitions team is learning fast under my mentorship.
We are women and we are free! Bringing an end to the patriarchy!
Just got my vaginal cone! Next level of pelvic floor!
I hate living opposite a liquor store! All I see when I look out the window is that crackhead Tonya!
You keep walkin with your nose in the air sooner or later u gonna take a fall.
I really love sushi now.
Makes a change to live on a block where the closest thing to gangbanging is rival book clubs!!

Big thanks to Bree and Kim for helping me making the hottest audition tape ever!
Just heard back from Weazel about the audition tape. I'm going on! Don't tell my parents.
Don't tell Mom and Dad about the auditions ok!
First time in Los Santos!!!
You have to get that psycho out of here. Debra will kill me.

Can't believe your folks sprung you for all that green!
oh great uncle trevor's back

I have to say your home life is not that zen
Just when I think hell can't get any worse, in walks the devil.
I'm thinking I should maybe get away, make a fresh start.
I'm still amazed to find possibly the most antisocial luddite in history on here.
You'll thank me for anaesthetizing you one day, I promise. I hope it gave you some perspective into how unbelievably fucked up our lives are. We all need some distance.
Looks like I'm officially from a broken home. Mom boned one guy too many. Dad brained one guy too many. It was only a matter of time.
I've moved out bitchzzz! J-Dog is roaming free!
How did that thing work out with your dad?
You've done the right thing. That man is a tangled ball of negative energy.

Please tell him to leave Mr Raspberry Jam alone! I'm begging you!

Has anyone got a sofa I can crash on?

Finally he's gone! Peace at last.

I just made the best shank ever.
It ain't gay if you're both straight.
Have you heard from Floyd or Debra recently?

u still owe me a 20 dog answer your phone!!!

Just let me know you're ok?

Physically assaulting annoying celebrities and yoga instructors! When it comes to father-son bonding that's so much more speed!
All those guy friends you've violently assaulted in the past and finally this time it might actually get me somewhere! Fame or Shame here I come!

We can do this. I know now that this family is too irreparably damaged to have any hope of a normal relationship with anyone else. We're stuck with each other. And that's as close to a "I love you" as I've been in a very long time.
My Mom & Dad are back together! And I made it to the finals of Fame or Shame on pure talent alone!
I'm totally going to college as soon as I'm done with the celebrity thing.
Dad beat up mom's boy toy with a laptop so I'm moving back home! Who's online later for some Slaughter time???

Giving it another try. He's a philandering selfish untrustworthy psychopath of a man, but he's my philandering selfish untrustworthy psychopath.
Now that I'm almost famous and have stalkers and shit, this psycho-over-protective-dad routine is finally starting pay dividends. Love you, Pop. xx
I have stalkers now! #priceoffame

how's it going on the outside? You seein to business?

Jimmy might actually get a job and Tracey might actually go college. What is going on???
I'm a movie producer's wife now :)
Just heard about Molly. Let me know how you want to move on this.
Molly, you were one of the most committed and ruthless lawyers I've ever had on my books. I promise you that your death will not be in vain.

Looks like another tantric evening for one :-)

Wow you actually stepped up and did something not cowardly for once in your life.
I'm a hero! I teabagged an elite special forces assassin and not just virtually in a game this time!
Everybody go see Meltdown! It's so awful it's awesome!

So now we're running strategy meetings from a strip club? You're really letting Philips run with the ball these days.
You can retire for real this time, old friend.
